" F6运行到下个断点
nmap <silent> <F6> <Plug>VimspectorRunToCursor
" F4 关闭debug
nmap <silent> <F4> :VimspectorReset<CR>


" =================== preservim/nerdtree =====================
" NERDTree配置(目录树) preservim/nerdtree
" NERDTree配置 打开侧边目录
nmap <silent><Esc><C-n> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
